'''丙型流感病毒'''（英文：Influenza C virus）是一种[[流感病毒|流感病毒]]，也是[[正黏液病毒科|正黏液病毒科]]丙型流感病毒屬（Gammainfluenzavirus）中的一[[种|种]]，可引起[[流行性感冒|流行性感冒]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Taxonomy browser (Gammainfluenzavirus)|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/Taxonomy/Browser/wwwtax.cgi?mode=Info&id=197913&lvl=3&lin=f&keep=1&srchmode=1&unlock|accessdate=2021-01-06|work=www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov}}</ref> 丙型流感病毒可感染人类和[[猪属|猪]]。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Isolation of Influenza C Virus from Pigs and Experimental Infection of Pigs with Influenza C Virus|author=|url=|journal=Journal of General Virology|issue=|doi=10.1099/0022-1317-64-1-177|others=|year=1983|volume=64|page=|pages=177–82|pmid=6296296|author3=Wang P.|author4=Wang M.|author5=Zhu J.M.|author1=Guo Y.|author2=Jin F.}}</ref>

丙型病毒拥有7个单链[[RNA|RNA]]片段，而甲型和乙型病毒则拥有8个单链RNA片段。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Influenza C Virus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/biochemistry-genetics-and-molecular-biology/influenza-c-virus|accessdate=2021-01-06|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect Topics|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119213842/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/biochemistry-genetics-and-molecular-biology/influenza-c-virus|dead-url=no}}</ref> 丙型流感病毒上只有一类凸起[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]（HEF蛋白），负责与[[受体_(生物化学)|受体]]结合。<ref name=":0" /> 无进一步亚型/支系分类。<ref>{{Cite web|title=流感高发！关于流感病毒你应该知道的N个真相！|url=http://www.ioz.cas.cn/kxcb/kpwz/201801/t20180116_4934511.html|accessdate=2021-01-06|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=中国科学院动物研究所|language=|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119213905/http://www.ioz.cas.cn/kxcb/kpwz/201801/t20180116_4934511.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

相比起[[甲型流感病毒|甲型流感病毒]]和[[乙型流感病毒|乙型流感病毒]]，丙型流感病毒较不常见、流感[[症状|症状]]较为轻微，对[[公共卫生|公共卫生]]影响较小，但是亦可以造成地方性[[流行病|流行]]。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=季节性流感|url=https://www.who.int/zh/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/influenza-(seasonal)|accessdate=2021-01-06|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211222092817/https://www.who.int/zh/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/influenza-(seasonal)|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[血清学|血清学]]研究显示，丙型流感病毒在世界范围内都有分布，但大部分人在年纪较轻时就已经对此病毒产生了抗体，故再次感染和重症的风险较小。<ref name=":1" /> 截止目前，还未有人体的针对性[[疫苗|疫苗]]。<ref name="Influenzavirus C and D2">{{cite web|title=Influenza C and Influenza D Viruses|url=https://www.swinehealth.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Influenza-virus-C-IVC-and-influenza-virus-D-IVD.pdf|author=2016|access-date=28 September 2018|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119213828/https://www.swinehealth.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Influenza-virus-C-IVC-and-influenza-virus-D-IVD.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

